                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050220-44-off268 t18050220-44-cd269"></join>, and stealing therein two coats, value 2 l. 10 s. a pair of breeches, value 7 s. a gown, value 6 s. one sheet, value 9 s. a frock, value 5 s. a cloth, value 2 s. four handkerchiefs, value 5 s. two shifts, value 5 s. and a wrapper, value 9 d. the property of 
